track_notes:
From Dobson pass follow the Gpx tract lots of other roads come off the main road not much for signage.  The road is accessible by 2WD vehicle to the TH rough in spots. At the saddle the road turns to a hairpin to the left find a wide spot and park at the corner.  From there to the summit is a half mile cross country follow the ridge.

Verizon available on top
